    <title>Hello World</title>
    <url>/2023/05/14/hello-world/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>Welcome to <a class="link"   href="https://hexo.io/" >Hexo</a>! This is your very first post. Check <a class="link"   href="https://hexo.io/docs/" >documentation</a> for more info. If you get any problems when using Hexo, you can find the answer in <a class="link"   href="https://hexo.io/docs/troubleshooting.html" >troubleshooting</a> or you can ask me on <a class="link"   href="https://github.com/hexojs/hexo/issues" >GitHub</a>.</p>
<h2 id="Quick-Start">Quick Start</h2>
<h3 id="Create-a-new-post">Create a new post</h3>
<div class="highlight-container" data-rel="Bash"><figure class="iseeu highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo new <span class="string">&quot;My New Post&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>
<p>More info: <a class="link"   href="https://hexo.io/docs/writing.html" >Writing</a></p>
<h3 id="Run-server">Run server</h3>
<div class="highlight-container" data-rel="Bash"><figure class="iseeu highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>
<p>More info: <a class="link"   href="https://hexo.io/docs/server.html" >Server</a></p>
<h3 id="Generate-static-files">Generate static files</h3>
<div class="highlight-container" data-rel="Bash"><figure class="iseeu highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo generate</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>
<p>More info: <a class="link"   href="https://hexo.io/docs/generating.html" >Generating</a></p>
<h3 id="Deploy-to-remote-sites">Deploy to remote sites</h3>
<div class="highlight-container" data-rel="Bash"><figure class="iseeu highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo deploy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>
<p>More info: <a class="link"   href="https://hexo.io/docs/one-command-deployment.html" >Deployment</a></p>
]]></content>
  </entry>
  <entry>
    <title>流萤与星空</title>
    <url>/2023/06/04/%E6%B5%81%E8%90%A4%E4%B8%8E%E6%98%9F%E7%A9%BA/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<iframe frameborder="no" border="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" width=330 height=86 src="//music.163.com/outchain/player?type=2&id=1426611455&auto=0&height=66"></iframe>
<p>流萤是明灭迷离、天真奇丽的憧憬尘埃是虚无纷飞，终将落地的厚重<sup class="footnote-ref"><a href="#fn1" id="fnref1">[1]</a></sup></p>
<p>腐草为萤也 飞萤缀于地流光为星也 群星饰于天</p>
<p>星空什么也不代表，但它代表了一切浪漫与憧憬。</p>
<p>若是来人能漫步于群星之间，他们的胸膛会灼热吗？如果古人尝试触摸星穹一角，他们的眼睛会闪烁吗？</p>
<p>流萤自于地上的尘埃，群星成于宇宙的尘埃</p>
<p>浮游的流萤，飘散的群星</p>
<p>星星是漫游者的灯塔</p>
<p>缀满天地时空的模糊光点，雨点落入浅海的无数涟漪，此身坠入梦境的触觉振动，流萤飞进最纯净澄澈的幻想</p>
<hr class="footnotes-sep">
<section class="footnotes">
<ol class="footnotes-list">
<li id="fn1" class="footnote-item"><p>改编自歌曲文案 <a href="#fnref1" class="footnote-backref">↩︎</a></p>
</li>
</ol>
</section>
]]></content>
